1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 26 MRSA §850-M, sub-§1-A is enacted to read:
3 1-A. State tax. An individual filing a new claim for family leave benefits or medical
4 leave benefits under this subchapter may elect to have the administrator deduct and
