3333 program are subject to state income tax to the extent those benefits are not included in the
3344 taxpayer's federal adjusted gross income. It also provides that a taxpayer's federal adjusted
3355 gross income may be reduced by the amount subject to repayment that has been previously
3366 taxed by the State. It also allows individuals filing a new claim for family leave benefits or
